33:58.655 --> 33:59.689
- Start knocking on doors?

33:59.758 --> 34:01.551
- Fuck that!

34:01.620 --> 34:04.482
I'm not going around like
a goddamn Jehovah Witness.

34:07.275 --> 34:10.206
- You're pretty quick
to surrender, amigo.

34:10.275 --> 34:12.620
'Cause I think
I recognize our bikes.

34:41.034 --> 34:41.965
- What's the Pashto for--

34:42.034 --> 34:44.000
- Who the fuck knows?

34:44.068 --> 34:45.793
He don't speak English.
Why didn't you bring Khalil?

34:45.862 --> 34:47.275
- He refused to come.

34:47.344 --> 34:48.724
He said venturing out here
without a convoy

34:48.793 --> 34:49.758
would be suicide.

34:49.827 --> 34:51.586
- Thanks for passing that on.

34:51.655 --> 34:53.068
- I didn't see any reason
to invite an unwanted

34:53.137 --> 34:55.448
cloud of doubt
over this operation, okay?

35:06.344 --> 35:08.275
- I ain't handing over shit.

35:08.344 --> 35:10.517
- Basis of all business
transactions is trust.

35:10.586 --> 35:11.896
- Not in my neighborhood.

35:11.965 --> 35:14.172
- Look...

35:14.241 --> 35:16.931
either we're doing this,
or we're not.

35:28.068 --> 35:29.758
Why you so worried?

35:39.793 --> 35:41.068
- [speaks Pashto]

35:49.413 --> 35:51.758
- He remind you of anyone?

35:51.827 --> 35:53.103
- Male or female?

35:53.172 --> 35:54.517
- Not gonna dignify that
with a response.

35:54.586 --> 35:55.896
- Skip through
the 20 questions.

35:55.965 --> 35:57.551
Just get to it, amigo.
- Sasquatch.

35:57.620 --> 35:59.000
They're both about
the same size, right?

35:59.068 --> 36:00.517
- Oh, it'd be so sweet
to see somebody

36:00.586 --> 36:01.896
knock that son of a bitch down.

36:01.965 --> 36:03.965
- Fight like that,
we'd clean up.

36:04.034 --> 36:05.413
Get us out of that hole
you put us in

36:05.482 --> 36:07.758
when Sasquatch
whooped your ass.

36:07.827 --> 36:09.379
- You think he'd be game?

36:09.448 --> 36:13.000
- Look to me like
he'd take some convincing.

36:13.068 --> 36:15.000
- Hey. Do you fight?

36:15.068 --> 36:16.689
You box?

36:16.758 --> 36:18.000
Do you box a little bit?

36:18.068 --> 36:19.482
You know
what I'm talking about?

36:19.551 --> 36:21.034
- Hey, knock it off.

36:21.103 --> 36:22.586
He's gonna think
you're really trying to fight.

36:22.655 --> 36:25.413
- You understand?
Fight?

36:25.482 --> 36:29.241
Whoa.
[laughs]

36:29.310 --> 36:30.655
- As-salaam alaikum.

36:30.724 --> 36:31.655
both: Wa-alaikum salaam.

36:31.724 --> 36:35.206
- [speaking Pashto]

36:40.482 --> 36:41.482
[ominous music]

36:44.517 --> 36:46.241
- What was he saying?
- I don't know.

36:46.310 --> 36:49.379
I'm tracking dirt
all over his rugs.

36:49.448 --> 36:52.379
- [speaking Pashto]

36:52.448 --> 36:55.517
♪ ♪

36:58.000 --> 37:00.896
- You're welcome.

37:00.965 --> 37:02.517
- That should hold you
until Obamacare

37:02.586 --> 37:05.000
makes its way
through these parts.

37:07.206 --> 37:09.206
[goat bleats]

37:22.344 --> 37:24.758
- Hey.

37:24.827 --> 37:27.344
[laughs]

37:27.413 --> 37:28.689
Hey.

37:30.655 --> 37:32.034
Who are you?

37:32.103 --> 37:35.724
- This goat
is touched in the head.

37:35.793 --> 37:37.413
- You speak English?

37:37.482 --> 37:39.310
- And French and German.

37:39.379 --> 37:40.448
- Is he yours?

37:40.517 --> 37:42.241
- It belongs to no one.

37:42.310 --> 37:44.413
Some think it is possessed
by spirits.

37:44.482 --> 37:46.068
- What's gonna happen to it?

37:46.137 --> 37:48.000
- It was raised
to be slaughtered for food,

37:48.068 --> 37:49.448
but the man
who owns it believes

37:49.517 --> 37:51.103
that if he were
to eat this goat,

37:51.172 --> 37:53.827
he would also be possessed
by those spirits.

37:53.896 --> 37:56.310
So he set it free.

37:56.379 --> 37:58.000
The man is an idiot.

37:58.068 --> 37:59.172
- It's a lucky goat.

37:59.241 --> 38:01.482
- No. No one here is lucky.

38:01.551 --> 38:05.034
This goat will eventually be
killed and eaten by wild boars.

38:07.310 --> 38:11.620
- [speaking Pashto]

38:11.689 --> 38:13.517
- Okay.

38:13.586 --> 38:16.586
- [speaking Pashto]

38:22.379 --> 38:26.379
[speaking Pashto]

38:30.517 --> 38:32.620
- Grade-A Afghan hashish.

38:32.689 --> 38:35.793
I ain't going anywhere
until we sample this shit.

38:35.862 --> 38:36.862
- Well,
since you're one of those

38:36.931 --> 38:38.310
"my body is God's temple" types

38:38.379 --> 38:40.000
and mine's a 7-Eleven,
I guess that's me?

38:40.068 --> 38:41.137
- Mm-hmm.

38:41.206 --> 38:43.103
- Yeah.

38:43.172 --> 38:46.862
- Who's a good boy?
You're a good boy.

38:46.931 --> 38:48.517
- Can you please tell me
what has happened

38:48.586 --> 38:50.379
to my brother Qasem?

38:50.448 --> 38:53.965
He was injured the other night
and taken to your base.

38:54.034 --> 38:55.379
- I don't know
anything about that.

38:55.448 --> 38:57.793
- I only need to know
if he's alive.

38:59.206 --> 39:00.379
- Look...

39:02.965 --> 39:05.034
I could find out for you.
Maybe.

39:05.103 --> 39:06.896
- Yes, thank you.

39:06.965 --> 39:09.206
I will now leave you alone
with your new boz.

39:09.275 --> 39:10.758
- Boz?

39:10.827 --> 39:12.137
- Boz.

39:14.206 --> 39:15.344
- Boz.

39:17.482 --> 39:19.517
You're possessed by spirits.

39:19.586 --> 39:21.241
That's so fucking cool.

39:31.655 --> 39:34.034
- We good?

39:34.103 --> 39:36.827
- [laughs]

39:36.896 --> 39:39.000
- I can't feel my legs.

39:39.068 --> 39:41.758
- [speaking Pashto]

39:41.827 --> 39:43.034
[ominous music]

39:43.103 --> 39:45.862
- Whoa.

39:45.931 --> 39:48.482
- [speaking Pashto]

39:50.379 --> 39:52.379
- Just the one brick?

39:52.448 --> 39:53.413
We had a deal.

39:53.482 --> 39:55.241
- Whoa, whoa, wait, Davis.

39:55.310 --> 39:56.620
I'm sure
we can figure this out.

39:56.689 --> 39:58.310
- He's got enough
antibiotics in there

39:58.379 --> 40:00.275
for every man, woman,
and child in this village.

40:00.344 --> 40:01.965
The animals, too.

40:02.034 --> 40:04.965
- [speaking Pashto]

40:05.034 --> 40:06.931
- Yeah, you better
put him back.

40:07.000 --> 40:08.206
This is some bullshit.

40:08.275 --> 40:11.379
- [shouting in Pashto]

40:14.655 --> 40:16.965
♪ ♪

40:17.034 --> 40:19.206
- I gotta be honest.

40:19.275 --> 40:20.689
I'm pretty fucked up right now.

40:24.655 --> 40:27.793
- Correction. The basis of all
getting fucked is trust.

40:27.862 --> 40:29.241
- Look, let's just take
one brick and go.

40:29.310 --> 40:31.068
- No.
I didn't come all the way here

40:31.137 --> 40:32.344
from the Southside of Chicago

40:32.413 --> 40:33.965
to get ripped off
by drug dealers.

40:34.034 --> 40:35.551
I could've done that
back in the hood.

40:35.620 --> 40:38.068
- Okay, okay, okay.

40:38.137 --> 40:41.068
[suspenseful music]

40:41.137 --> 40:43.000
♪ ♪

40:43.068 --> 40:45.000
Everybody cool?

40:45.068 --> 40:47.310
♪ ♪

40:47.379 --> 40:49.000
- [speaks Pashto]

40:49.068 --> 40:51.689
♪ ♪

40:51.758 --> 40:52.965
- I'm gonna torch this shit.

40:53.034 --> 40:54.931
- [yelling in Pashto]

40:56.862 --> 40:58.344
- Now...

40:58.413 --> 41:01.103
amigo, grab the box,
and get in the ambulance.

41:01.172 --> 41:02.241
- I ain't leaving without you.

41:02.310 --> 41:04.137
- Now, you know

41:04.206 --> 41:05.931
that there is plenty more
medicine where this came from,

41:06.000 --> 41:07.862
and I know that
that box of hashish

41:07.931 --> 41:09.413
couldn't have set you back
more than a couple of Afghanis

41:09.482 --> 41:10.931
to produce.

41:11.000 --> 41:12.758
So it's time to do the math,
Your Honor.

41:12.827 --> 41:15.862
Or Your Excellency or whatever.

41:15.931 --> 41:18.482
- [speaking Pashto]

41:18.551 --> 41:20.931
- Yeah.

41:21.000 --> 41:23.551
I just realized
I'm holding iodine.

41:23.620 --> 41:25.758
It's not flammable.
I'm pretty high.

41:25.827 --> 41:28.103
- Let's go before
they realize it, too.

41:30.275 --> 41:33.827
- [shouting in Pashto]

41:33.896 --> 41:38.000
♪ ♪

41:38.068 --> 41:39.965
- Take this.

41:40.034 --> 41:46.586
♪ ♪

41:48.275 --> 41:50.000
Where the hell is Petrocelli?

41:50.068 --> 41:51.482
- What part
of "stay in the ambulance"

41:51.551 --> 41:53.068
did he not fucking get?

41:58.068 --> 42:00.172
[goat bleats]

42:05.896 --> 42:07.551
- Oh, wow.

42:11.068 --> 42:13.172
You were thirsty, weren't you?

42:16.000 --> 42:18.931
[dramatic music]

42:19.000 --> 42:25.103
♪ ♪

42:25.172 --> 42:28.862
Oh. I hope you remember
which way we came from.

42:28.931 --> 42:31.689
'Cause I sure don't.

42:31.758 --> 42:35.206
♪ ♪

42:35.275 --> 42:36.620
- Drop your weapon.
Put your hands up.

42:36.689 --> 42:38.655
Identify yourself.

42:38.724 --> 42:43.034
- Private Anthony Petrocelli!
United States Army!

42:43.103 --> 42:44.862
That's not my goat, I...

42:44.931 --> 42:46.137
- You lost?

42:46.206 --> 42:48.655
- Uh... I...

42:48.724 --> 42:51.310
- Think he was talking
to the goat.

42:51.379 --> 42:53.275
- What the fuck
are you doing here, Roback?

42:53.344 --> 42:55.827
- There's a great little place
here that has the best kebabs.

42:55.896 --> 42:57.275
You good?
- Am I gonna get in trouble?

42:57.344 --> 42:59.344
- No. These guys
have no authority over us.

42:59.413 --> 43:02.034
- You told me
the entire area was secure.

43:02.103 --> 43:03.517
Is there a problem?

43:03.586 --> 43:06.517
- No problem.
Should be moving along shortly.

43:06.586 --> 43:07.655
- Glad to hear it.

43:09.551 --> 43:12.551
- Who the fuck's that guy?
Looks really important.

43:12.620 --> 43:14.310
- Heard Major Holloway
confined you to base,

43:14.379 --> 43:15.551
so you being out here
is a clear violation

43:15.620 --> 43:16.965
of a direct order.

43:17.034 --> 43:18.379
- You're not gonna tell on me,
are you?

43:18.448 --> 43:21.551
- You men need to stay
far away from here.

43:21.620 --> 43:23.137
- Why would we do that?

43:25.275 --> 43:28.241
- You're so far over your head,
Roback, you have no idea.

43:28.310 --> 43:29.448
[horn honks]

43:31.551 --> 43:34.517
- Sounds like you better
get going.

43:34.586 --> 43:37.482
[suspenseful music]

43:37.551 --> 43:39.344
♪ ♪

43:39.413 --> 43:41.689
The fuck was that?
A fucking dance move?

43:41.758 --> 43:43.689
[engine turns over]

43:45.896 --> 43:50.758
♪ ♪

43:50.827 --> 43:52.517
- What was that all about?

43:52.586 --> 43:54.517
- Who gives a shit?

43:54.586 --> 43:56.379
Better get back to base
before my absence is felt.

43:56.448 --> 43:58.448
- Where the hell are we?

44:01.931 --> 44:03.724
- Came from that way.

44:06.793 --> 44:09.931
- So are you guys ready to tell
me what it is we're doing here?

44:10.000 --> 44:11.379
both: No!

44:13.793 --> 44:16.413
♪ ♪

44:16.482 --> 44:18.482
- Where's Boz?

44:22.206 --> 44:24.103
- Motherfuck!

44:24.172 --> 44:25.620
- Who did this?

44:25.689 --> 44:27.724
- If it was Taliban,
we'd all be dead.

44:27.793 --> 44:29.206
- Oh, God.

44:29.275 --> 44:30.931
- Now we got no way
to get back,

44:31.000 --> 44:32.275
the sun's going down,

44:32.344 --> 44:33.724
and we're not even
supposed to be here.

44:33.793 --> 44:35.586
- Not to mention
the 10 pounds of hashish

44:35.655 --> 44:38.344
we got strapped to our backs.

44:38.413 --> 44:41.000
- Hashish?

44:41.068 --> 44:42.931
- Let's do this.

44:43.000 --> 44:45.793
- I signed that ambulance out
under my name.

44:45.862 --> 44:47.586
They are gonna make pay for it,
aren't they?

44:47.655 --> 44:49.862
- Kid, on the slim chance
we make it back to base alive,

44:49.931 --> 44:51.310
they're gonna make us all pay.

44:51.379 --> 44:52.655
Come on.
